### Test 1: Request without token (should return 401 Unauthorized)
GET http://localhost:5077/blogs

### Test 2: Request with invalid token format (should return 401 Unauthorized)
GET http://localhost:5077/blogs
Authorization: InvalidToken

### Test 3: Get all blogs with valid token
GET http://localhost:5077/blogs
Authorization: Bearer valid-secret-token-12345

### Test 4: Get blog by ID with valid token
GET http://localhost:5077/blogs/0
Authorization: Bearer valid-secret-token-12345

### Test 5: Get blog by ID (not found) with valid token
GET http://localhost:5077/blogs/10
Authorization: Bearer valid-secret-token-12345

### Test 6: Create a new blog with valid token
POST http://localhost:5077/blogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer valid-secret-token-12345

{
  "title": "Third Blog Post",
  "body": "This is the content of the third blog post"
}

### Test 7: Create another blog with valid token
POST http://localhost:5077/blogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer valid-secret-token-12345

